            "main_product_faq_NbeGD7": {
              "type": "_main_product__faq",
              "name": "FAQ",
              "settings": {
                "question_1": "How do I use Restore?",
                "answer_1": "<p>Mix one stick (or one scoop from the bag) with 8–12 oz of cold water once daily. Best taken on an empty stomach in the morning, or 30 minutes before bed for overnight hydration and recovery.</p>",
                "question_2": "When will I feel results?",
                "answer_2": "<p><strong>Day 1:</strong> immediate hydration and sharper focus.<br/><strong>4–6 weeks:</strong> fewer sick days, better detox.<br/><strong>8–10 weeks:</strong> deeper cellular energy and mental clarity.<br/><strong>12–14 weeks:</strong> visible changes in skin hydration, elasticity, and brightness.</p>",
                "question_3": "What's inside Restore?",
                "answer_3": "<p>Capsoil® Liposomal Vitamin C, Capsoil® Liposomal Glutathione, Nanoemulsified CoQ10, a methylated B-vitamin complex, and a mineral &amp; electrolyte blend delivering 920mg of electrolytes per serving. No added sugar. No bloating.</p>",
                "question_4": "Bags vs. Sticks — what's the difference?",
                "answer_4": "<p>Same formula. Bags are the best value per serving and easiest at home. Sticks are single-serve, TSA-friendly, and built for travel, the gym, or the office.</p>",
                "question_5": "Can I take Restore before bed?",
                "answer_5": "<p>Yes. You lose up to a liter of water overnight through breathing and skin. Restore before bed keeps hydration and mineral balance steady through the night and supports natural overnight detoxification.</p>",
                "question_6": "How is Restore different from greens powders or sports drinks?",
                "answer_6": "<p>Greens powders pack dozens of ingredients at doses too small to do anything. Sports drinks deliver electrolytes with sugar and bloating. Restore uses fewer ingredients at clinically meaningful doses, with pharmaceutical-grade delivery systems so they actually reach your bloodstream.</p>",
                "question_7": "Is Restore third-party tested?",
                "answer_7": "<p>Yes. Every batch is third-party tested for purity, heavy metals, and contaminants. No artificial colors, no added sugar, no proprietary blends.</p>",
                "question_8": "",
                "answer_8": ""
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
